extends ../layout

block content
	.row
		h2 Unit 1 | Fruits
		b 1. I am medium size and round. I can be red, green or yellow. What am I?
		span(style="display:block")
				div
					input(type="radio", id="Apple", name="unit-1-1", value="1")
					| Apple <br/>
					input(type="radio", id="Pear", name="unit-1-1", value="2")
					| Pear <br/>
					input(type="radio", id="Guava", name="unit-1-1", value="3")
					| Guava <br/>
		b 2. I am small and red. Many people like me. What am I?
		span(style="display:block")
				div
					input(type="radio", id="Apple", name="unit-1-2", value="1")
					| Blueberry <br/>
					input(type="radio", id="Pear", name="unit-1-2", value="2")
					| Lemon <br/>
					input(type="radio", id="Guava", name="unit-1-2", value="3")
					| Strawberry <br/>
		b 3. I am brown on outside and yellow inside. I am big and prickly. I have big prickly leaves growing on top of me. What am I? 
		span(style="display:block")
				div
					input(type="radio", id="Apple", name="unit-1-3", value="1")
					| Kiwi <br/>
					input(type="radio", id="Pear", name="unit-1-3", value="2")
					| Pineapple <br/>
					input(type="radio", id="Guava", name="unit-1-3", value="3")
					| Banana <br/>
		b 4. I am yellow and medium size. I taste sour. What am I?
		span(style="display:block")
				div
					input(type="radio", id="Apple", name="unit-1-4", value="1")
					| Pinapple <br/>
					input(type="radio", id="Pear", name="unit-1-4", value="2")
					| Banana <br/>
					input(type="radio", id="Guava", name="unit-1-4", value="3")
					| Lemon <br/>
		b 5. I am brown on outside and green inside. I am hairy on outside. I can taste sweet or sour. What am I?
		span(style="display:block")
				div
					input(type="radio", id="Apple", name="unit-1-5", value="1")
					| Pineapple <br/>
					input(type="radio", id="Pear", name="unit-1-5", value="2")
					| Kiwi <br/>
					input(type="radio", id="Guava", name="unit-1-5", value="3")
					| Coconut <br/>

		br
		button.btn.btn-success.btn-md(type="submit") Check